  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Désirée is situated in the heart of Sirmione’s historical old town surrounded by parks and gardens creating a tranquil and relaxing environment. A short walk from the shops and cafés of the resort and close to the famous Grottos of Catullo it offers superb panoramic views and comfortable accommodation. This idyllic hotel provides a perfect location to explore Sirmione and Lake Garda.</p>]]></description>
